  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MapsActivity
    Activity where the user can view a map that displays the locations of their habit events as well as the habit events of who they're following
    NotificationAdapter
    This an extension of the ArrayAdapter class that is compatible with the custom format of the notification list
    NotificationsActivity
    Activity where the user can view their list of notifications.
    Permissions
    This class has all static methods and is meant to act as a toolbox for requesting permissions from Android.

    This is a static class that provides a toolbox for saving locally and to ElasticSearch.
